Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:20.16,Episode-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就告別了今日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:20.16,Episode-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今日の日はさようなら
